data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  Welcome to the Gated, Solar Panel Community of Innovation at Hidden Lake. Take a leisurely stroll down the wandering docks kissing the shores of Johns Lake. Feel like going home for lunch by boat? No problem with the inviting community dock. You really can have it all;  cozy up to nature while staying close to shopping and entertainment. This home embodies the love of a big family with its 5 bedrooms 2 1/2 baths. From the cozy front porch to the large fenced in back yard, lots of quality family time is calling your name.  Downstairs you will find a well appointed decorator detail hallway entrance with stunning light accents leading to the custom designed stacked-bunk bedroom with built in homework desk, 1/2 bath, continue on  to the beautiful kitchen which brightens up your day with white quartz countertops and basket weave tile accents on the front of the kitchen island, 42" cabinets,   stainless steel appliances, double oven for the at home chef, walk in pantry, breakfast bar, open floor plan dining area and large family room.  Upstairs you land at the loft for TV -a 1 on 1 board game challenge, a quick read etc. 3 bedrooms share a large bathroom with dual sinks and separate water closet and shower. The Owner's Suite -offers a large bathroom and super-sized closet, because don't forget shopping is close by. This home sits on 1 of only 2 corner lots in the neighborhood adding additional privacy and large backyard with evening lighting for those that enjoy the outside after the sun has gone down .  Close to all major theme park attractions, commuting highways, downtown Clermont or downtown Winter Garden are all within an easy drive. ( Please note 2 photos are virtually staged)
